<h3><strong>Gary &amp; Lora Rozkowski</strong></h3><p><img src="https://worshipwarriors.net/images/h3bg.gif"></p><p><img src="https://worshipwarriors.net/images/t_us-2023a.jpg" alt="Gary &amp; Lora [The Roz's]" width="228" height="400"></p><p><span style="font-size:11px;">PHOTO: Gary &amp; I at our nephew's wedding, in sunny Florida.</span></p><p>"Gary and I have lived in the Tampa Bay area of Florida for 35+&nbsp;years, and originally from Detroit, Michigan. &nbsp;We share our home with our little dogs; Ridley &amp; Ruby and our cute parakeet David (pronounced: Da Veed).&nbsp;</p><p>With awe, we see God's purpose and destiny for our lives unfold before us, more and more every day. &nbsp;Serving the LORD as International Chaplains, and in our local church, the expectation to see God move mightily in other's lives, is our constant prayer.&nbsp;</p><p>Yeshua Messiah has made everything we are and everything we do... possible. Click on our testimonies below to read how our lives have changed for eternity."</p><p><img src="https://worshipwarriors.net/images/MESSIANIC/tt_website-shalom.png" alt="SHALOM" width="31" height="14"> (Shalom), Lora</p><h3><strong>PERSONAL TESTIMONIES</strong></h3><p>&nbsp;&nbsp; <img src="https://worshipwarriors.net/images/bullet.gif"> <a href="https://worshipwarriors.net/misc/lora-testimony.pdf">Lora's Testimony</a></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp; <img src="https://worshipwarriors.net/images/bullet.gif"> <a href="https://worshipwarriors.net/misc/gary-testimony.pdf">Gary's Testimony</a></p><h3><strong>MINISTRY</strong></h3><p>&nbsp;&nbsp; <img src="https://worshipwarriors.net/images/bullet.gif"> Lora Rozkowski is an International Chaplain, licensed minister,&nbsp;and business owner. <a href="https://worshipwarriors.net/PDF/Minister-Lora-BIO.pdf">Ministry - BIO</a></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp; <img src="https://worshipwarriors.net/images/bullet.gif"> Gary Rozkowski is an International Chaplain, and licensed minister.&nbsp; <a href="https://worshipwarriors.net/PDF/Minister-Gary-BIO.pdf">Ministry - BIO</a></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp; <img src="https://worshipwarriors.net/images/bullet.gif"> This is our Missions News:&nbsp;<a href="https://worshipwarriors.net/index.php?main_page=page_3">Roz's Mission News</a></p>